  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下这次WAF部署的流量走向图。核心是一个Azure订阅，里面放Application Gateway，然后要体现跟本地数据中心的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Application Gateway",
        "WAF",
        "On-Prem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Azure内部结构需要细化吗？比如VNet和子网的层级？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VNet",
        "Subnets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要的。VNet用10.10.0.0/16，子网分成web、app、db、mgmt四个。另外Azure外面两边，一边是Internet，一边是On-Prem——我们这边用VyOS做网关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VNet: 10.10.0.0/16",
        "Subnets: web/app/db/mgmt",
        "Internet",
        "On-Prem (VyOS + VMs)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先搭个框架：Azure订阅作为子图，里面放资源组、VNet和子网。外面左右分别是Internet和On-Prem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Resource Group",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets",
        "Internet",
        "On-Prem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但资源组那个框用花括号标注一下，表示这是逻辑容器。然后VNet和子网的关系要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Resource Group",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整好了。现在画连接关系：Internet到VNet是单向流量，On-Prem到VNet是双向的，用VPN或者ExpressRoute那种感觉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "VNet",
        "On-Prem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Internet到VNet的箭头方向反了。应该是Internet指向VNet，表示外部流量进入Azure。你刚才可能画成双向了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "VNet"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修正了，Internet → VNet是单向进入。On-Prem那边保持双向箭头，表示两边都有主动发起的流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "VNet",
